    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.86 - v2 + 0.84) * (tmp + 0.46 + tmp + 0.09)))
    v1 = ((v2 * (v0 + 0.07 * v0 + 0.18)) / wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.05)))
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.81 - tmp + 0.79) / v2))
    v0 = tmp
